      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "We're using `pandoc` utility tool for\ngenerating the md -> Pdf, Word, Txt\n\nuse pandoc + MiKTeX to generate the\nbeautiful exports like latex overleaf\npdf export\nrest docx and plain text are eaisly\nhandled by the padoc itself",
